---
title: Dynamite Mushroom & Shrimp Tempura with Roasted Green Beans & Zesty Rice
description: One of our favorite ways to eat our veggies? Giving them the tempura treatment! Coating them in the light, airy batter before frying yields addictively crispy, golden results you just can’t get any other way. Here, you’ll whip up tempura mushrooms, then pile them into rice bowls with tender roasted green beans. It’s all drizzled with our favorite dynamite sauce—a creamy, spicy, sweet, and savory (yes, all those things!) sauce that’s so good, you’ll find yourself swiping up every last drop.
